; Coverage test for report.cc lines 942-951: fn_commodity_price
; Test commodity_price() which looks up a commodity's price at a given date.

P 2024/01/01 AAPL $100.00
P 2024/06/01 AAPL $150.00

2024/01/01 Buy
    Assets:Stock    10 AAPL
    Assets:Cash    $-1000.00

test reg Assets:Stock --format '%(commodity_price(amount, [2024/06/01]))\n'
$150.00
end test
